rows.label: qst103406_msg0001
rows.name: Are you safe?! How did it go...?

rows.label: qst103406_msg0002
rows.name:
Was Akatsuki's Driver not
among the Brionac leaders...?

rows.label: qst103406_msg0003
rows.name:
No... There is no need to
trouble yourselves any further.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0004
rows.name: Let us put an end to this matter.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0005
rows.name:
The subordinate who was gathering
intelligence for me was attacked...

rows.label: qst103406_msg0006
rows.name:
It may only be a matter of time
before they come after me or my son.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0007
rows.name:
We have defeated the leaders...
Sooner or later, Brionac's
plans should fall apart.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0009
rows.name:
However, to delve any
deeper would be...

rows.label: qst103406_msg0010
rows.name:
Then, from this point on, please
act on your own initiative.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0011
rows.name:
You will have to gather
information on Akatsuki
and his Driver yourselves.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0012
rows.name: I will have no involvement whatsoever.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0013
rows.name:
When I think of my son,
this is the only way...

rows.label: qst103406_msg0101
rows.name:
If possible, I would prefer
that you refrain from
speaking to me like this.

rows.label: qst103406_msg0102
rows.name:
I do not know when or where
someone might be watching...
